{"word":"G3421 - μνημονεύω - mnēmoneúō - mnay-mon-yoo'-o - Make mention; be mindful","slug":"G3421","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μνημονεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mnēmoneúō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mnay-mon-yoo'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Make mention; be mindful"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BC;&#x03BD;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03BF;&#x03BD;&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - mne&#x0304;moneuo&#x0304;</b> - <i>mnay-mon-yoo'-o</i><p/>From a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3420\">G3420</a>; to <i>exercise memory</i>, that is, <i>recollect</i>; by implication to <i>punish</i>; also to <i>rehearse:</i> - make mention, be mindful, remember."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3403\">G3403</a>, <a href=\"#/G3417\">G3417</a>, <a href=\"#/G3418\">G3418</a>, <a href=\"#/G3419\">G3419</a>, <a href=\"#/G3420\">G3420</a>, <a href=\"#/G3422\">G3422</a>"}]}